posts.post_content:
Have several SGC cards I’m trying to trade for PSA 3-4 cards to help upgrade my set. I’m interested in most, so shoot me a note of what you have and values, along with what you’re looking for. Will consider selling too, but hoping to make some trades.

Thanks for looking!

Jeff
